{
  "text": "LGN, V1 and the eccentricity values on V1 are computed using our previous technique proposed in [CITATION_1] ). This approach is based on [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] ) that is mentioned in section 2.2.1 and was used earlier to identify the sub bundles of the optic radiation [CITATION_4] .",
